B2. Per-Entity Reduction Pipeline (Stages 2–5)

Important: The pipeline runs per entity (per phrase), not on all 691 CUIs combined. Each of the 25 phrases runs through Stages 2–5 independently. This means Stage 5 (Otsu + structural guards) runs 25 times — once per phrase. The 138 final CUIs are the union of all per-entity survivors.

The batch optimization is that metadata fetch (Stage 3) and embedding fetch are shared across all 25 phrases in a single BigQuery call. But the reduction logic itself is per-entity.

